 (AMP)</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Crew Health Care System (CHeCS)</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Advanced Life Support Pack (ALSP)</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Dental Kit</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Eye Kit</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">IV Kit</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Minor Surgery Kit</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.equipment.defibrillator-status\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for equipment.defibrillator-status </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Functional - tested</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Needs maintenance</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Non-functional</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">N/A</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.resupply.priority\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for resupply.priority </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Urgent - next available vehicle</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">High - within 60 days</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Normal - next planned resupply</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Low - can wait</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.summary.overall-status\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for summary.overall-status </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Adequate - no action needed</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Minor shortages - monitor</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Significant gaps - resupply needed</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Critical - immediate action required</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.data-delivery.archive\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for data-delivery.archive </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">https://mitre.org/fhir/space-health/CodeSystem/nasa-data-archive-cs#mmis (\"Medical Mission Information System\")</li></ul></div>"^^rdf:XMLLiteral ]
